[Comment "crush-the-slav-with-the-boor-attack/course/11611, variation/655709"]

1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Nc3 Nf6 5. f3 Nc6 6. e4 dxe4 7. d5 Ne5 8. fxe4 e6 
9. Nf3 Nxf3+ 10. Qxf3 exd5 11. e5 Ne4 12. Bb5+ Bd7 13. Rf1 f6 14. exf6 Nxf6 15. Qe2+ 
Qe7 {The correct defense.} 16. Bxd7+ Nxd7 17. Be3 O-O-O 18. O-O-O Nf6 19. Qf3 $14 
{White has excellent compensation for the pawn by way of full development and 
attacking chances. In my experience Black will suffer to make a draw (if he 
survives).} *

