1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 {The Exchange Variation of the Slav.} cxd5 4. Nc3 Nf6 5. f3 
$1 Nc6 6. e4 {A critical juncture. Black can now choose to close the game with e6 and 
suffer a cramped French style position or jump into the open game where tactics and 
initiative arm the well prepared white player.} dxe4 7. d5 *

