1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Nc3 Nf6 5. f3 Nc6 6. e4 e5 7. dxe5 Nxe5 8. f4 Nc6 
{A natural retreat seeking sharp gambit play. We will oblige !} 9. exd5 Nb4 10. Bb5+ 
Bd7 11. d6 {[%cal Bd6e7,Bd1e2] Jamming up black's development and creating deadly 
threats.} Bxb5 12. Nxb5 Qa5 13. Qe2+ Kd7 14. Nf3 Nd3+ 15. Kf1 Qxb5 16. Ne5+ Kxd6 17. 
Be3 $1 {Planning Rd1 with an excellent long term attack on the black king.} *

