does not prevent the e4 break.} dxe4 8. Bxf6 {An important intermezzo.} Nxf6 9. fxe4 
{[%cal Bf1b5,Bc3e4][%csl Bb5,Be4,Be8] Black is unable to recapture due to tactics on 
the a4-d7 diagonal. Black is faced with many attacks based on Bb5+ and pawn to e5.} *

