1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Nc3 Nf6 5. f3 Qb6 6. e3 Bf5 $2 {This only creates a 
target for us to attack.} 7. g4 $1 Bg6 8. h4 {If black plays h5 then pawn to g5 will 
win the d5 pawn.} h6 9. Nge2 $14 {[%cal Be2f4,Bg4g5,Bd3g6,Bf7g6][%csl Bf4,Bg6,Bd5] 
White will play Nf4 and have a very strong attack as Bh7 fails to prevent g5-g6. If 
black plays h5 then pawn to g5 will win the d5 pawn.} *

