Bxc3+ 9. bxc3 Qa5 {Black is forcing the play and attempting to win a pawn. Creating a 
Tal pawn with tempo. Qxc3 would exchange three pawns for a knight but also give white 
a winning attack.} 10. e5 Ne4 11. Bd2 b6 12. Bd3 Nxd2 13. Qxd2 Nc6 14. Nh3 $5 {[%cal 
Be1g1,Bh3f4,Bh3g5,Bf1f3] The white center is so strong we are afforded this luxurious 
move. The position is ready made for attacking.} *

